column5: Man, I am jacked to go fishing. I couldn't get out this past weekend do to a rally hI was involved with here in town. ( friends of Bill W thing)  All day Saturday, my friends were calling me saying: Fish ON !  Gonna go up this weekend if the rain doesnt blow the rivers around here again.

he's a good friend to have...wouldn't mind having him back.  good luck when you make it out.  i'm hoping to get out here around the Barrie area in the morning if the rain holds off and again wednesday
He's got "friends" in Barrie too.  i know two of them.. Butch and Eric
